OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773497488
OL,3,CNew archbishop set to make 87 mile
OL,4,Cpilgrimage from London to Canterbury
OL,6,FThe new Archbishop of Canterbury is to
OL,7,Fmake an 87-mile pilgrimage from London
OL,8,Fahead of her formal enthronement as
OL,9,Fthe top bishop in the Church of
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FDame Sarah Mullally, who was named
OL,13,Flast year as the first woman to take
OL,14,Fthe leading role, will also become the
OL,15,Ffirst Archbishop of Canterbury in
OL,16,Fmodern history to undertake the trek.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
