PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773497488
OL,3,CNew archbishop set to make 87 mile
OL,4,Cpilgrimage from London to Canterbury
OL,6,FShe will, alongside her husband
OL,7,FEamonn, begin the journey to
OL,8,FCanterbury on Tuesday, making their
OL,9,Fway along the Becket Camino route from
OL,10,FSt Paul's Cathedral in London to
OL,11,FCanterbury Cathedral.
OL,13,FDame Sarah, who was Bishop of London
OL,14,Ffor almost a decade, described it as
OL,15,F"deeply humbling to be following in
OL,16,Fthe footsteps of those who have walked
OL,17,Fthis ancient route."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773497488
OL,3,CNew archbishop set to make 87 mile
OL,4,Cpilgrimage from London to Canterbury
OL,6,FShe said: "For centuries, faithful
OL,7,Fpilgrims have flocked to Canterbury
OL,8,Fand I will be reflecting on this
OL,9,Ftradition as we make our way through
OL,10,Fthe Kent countryside and its towns and
OL,11,Fcities."
OL,13,FThe six-day journey, during which the
OL,14,FArchbishop will stop at various points
OL,15,Ffor prayer services at churches,
OL,16,Fcathedrals and abbeys, meet other
OL,17,Fpilgrims and visit schools and
OL,18,Fecumenical organisations, will end on
OL,19,FSunday March 22.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
