OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773497488
OL,3,CNew archbishop set to make 87 mile
OL,4,Cpilgrimage from London to Canterbury
OL,6,FDame Sarah will be formally installed,
OL,7,For enthroned, at Canterbury Cathedral
OL,8,Fon Wednesday March 25.
OL,10,FThe Prince of Wales will represent the
OL,11,FKing at the historic ceremony.
OL,13,FKing Charles is supreme governor of
OL,14,Fthe Church of England but William, his
OL,15,Fson and heir, will deputise for the
OL,16,Fhead of state at the service.
OL,18,FHe will be joined by the Princess of
OL,19,FWales.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
