OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773497488
OL,3,CNew archbishop set to make 87 mile
OL,4,Cpilgrimage from London to Canterbury
OL,6,FAs the ceremony marks the official
OL,7,Fstart of Dame Sarah's public ministry,
OL,8,Fshe will, for the first time, preach a
OL,9,Fsermon as Archbishop of Canterbury.
OL,11,FStops along her route will include
OL,12,FSouthwark Cathedral, Aylesford Priory,
OL,13,Fthe Shrine of St Jude in Faversham,
OL,14,FLesnes Abbey and Rochester Cathedral.
OL,16,FThe Dean of Canterbury, David
OL,17,FMonteith, is expected to join for the
OL,18,Ffinal stretch of the journey, walking
OL,19,Ffrom the village of Chartham to
OL,20,FCanterbury, and aiming to arrive in
OL,21,Ftime for evensong.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
