OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773497488
OL,3,CNew archbishop set to make 87 mile
OL,4,Cpilgrimage from London to Canterbury
OL,6,FDame Sarah said: "I'm looking forward
OL,7,Fto visiting local churches, cathedrals
OL,8,Fand holy sites along the route, and to
OL,9,Fmeeting people, praying with them and
OL,10,Fhearing their stories."
OL,12,F"As I walk this path I will be praying
OL,13,Ffor our Church and our world and
OL,14,Fasking God to bless those we meet.
OL,16,F"Every Christian life is a pilgrimage,
OL,17,Fa journey with God."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
